high_descs: Walk forward to the shelves then turn right and walk to the sink that's in front of you to your right.
Pick up the egg that's in front of you in the sink.
Turn right and walk to the microwave.
Cook the egg in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the table then turn right and walk to the stove then take a step to your left to face the green garbage.
Put the egg in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked egg in the garbage.

high_descs: Turn right and walk ahead, veering right to the sink.
Pick up the egg in the sink.
Heat the egg in the microwave.
Turn around and veer right, walking to the end of the counter.
Place the egg in the green bin on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked egg in a trash bin.

high_descs: Turn right, head to the sink on the other side of the room.
Pick up the egg in the sink.
Bring the egg to the microwave on the right.
Heat the egg in the microwave.
Take the heated egg, turn around, bring it to the green bin left of the stove.
Put the heated egg in the green bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated egg in the green bin.
